            <section ID="ID_EC14F390-B10C-A4EB-E558-F304BBCB4F51">
               <id root="59ee3304-bead-4015-8d0d-1e77f577aa65"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>FOR EXTERNAL USE ONLY<br/>NOT FOR OPHTHALMIC USE<br/>Rx Only<br/>
                  <br/>DESCRIPTION </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Triamcinolone Acetonide Cream USP contains triamcinolone acetonide [Pregna-1,4-diene-3,20-dione, 9-fluoro-11,21-dihydroxy-16,17-[(1-methylethylidene)bis- (oxy)]-, (11β,16α)-], with the empirical formula C<sub>24</sub>H<sub>31</sub>FO<sub>6</sub> and molecular weight 434.50. CAS 76-25-5.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="L3b184463-1a4b-4d19-aca5-61fe3a20cd0d"/>
                     <br/>
                     <br/>
                     <br/>Triamcinolone Acetonide Cream USP 0.025% contains: 0.25 mg of triamcinolone acetonide USP per gram in a water washable cream base consisting of  mineral oil (and) lanolin alcohol, isopropyl palmitate NF, propylene glycol stearate, propylene glycol USP, cetyl alcohol NF, sorbitan monostearate NF, polysorbate 60 NF, sorbic acid NF, polyoxyl (40) stearate NF, propylparaben NF, methylparaben NF and purified water USP. <br/>
                     <br/>Triamcinolone Acetonide Cream USP 0.1% contains: 1 mg of triamcinolone acetonide USP per gram in a water washable cream base consisting of  mineral oil (and) lanolin alcohol, isopropyl palmitate NF, propylene glycol stearate, propylene glycol USP, cetyl alcohol NF, sorbitan monostearate NF, polysorbate 60 NF, sorbic acid NF, polyoxyl (40) stearate NF, propylparaben NF, methylparaben NF and purified water USP.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20201005"/>
               <component>
                  <observationMedia ID="L3b184463-1a4b-4d19-aca5-61fe3a20cd0d">
                     <text>Triamcinolone Acetonide Cream-1</text>
                     <value mediaType="image/jpeg" xsi:type="ED">
                        <reference value="Triamcinolone Acetonide Cream-1.jpg"/>
                     </value>
                  </observationMedia>
               </component>
            </section>
